root: ^Socks and a hat... Those would have been nice... Probably  shouldn't have bet them, but I was so close!
^Oh well. It is what it is. I'll survive this week somehow.
^The socks and hat. Where did you get them?
^Are you an idiot? Why would I tell you?
^Hey, you got a deck? Money? You just came from the Big Land, didn't you? Got any tobacco? I will pay you back later this week, I swear, just gimme some already!
^Leave him alone! And get outta here already- you're empty! Come back when you've got something to bet, you useless piece of shit!
^And you, fresh boy, are you playing or what?
^Yes. I want those socks and hat back.
^Let's see if they will dance for you today!
